title: Duo Partner
body: I am looking for a duo partner to help me carry myself to silver. I want someone that is good at teamwork, is not toxic so pretty much a good team mate. Playing Mon-Friday 4pm to 5pm be on a little earlier than 4 so we can find a match early (about 3:50). Add me on curse if you have it I can use skype but I rarely use it now. Add me!
